"{\"uid\": \"channelstv.com-2024-07-16-paris-airport-staff-call-off-pre-olympics-strike\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Unions had called for a stoppage on Wednesday to press for bigger Olympics bonuses and staff recruitment.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 105, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris airport workers have called off a strike that would have disrupted travel just ahead of the Olympic Games after reaching a deal on bonuses, labour and management said Tuesday.\", \"from\": 109, \"to\": 290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 109, \"end\": 114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999188276, \"rank\": 8.118055888728175e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The deal \\\"was finalised today between three representative unions and ADP management,\\\" said the airport company, which is 50.6-percent controlled by the French state.\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 458, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 445, \"end\": 451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9720360590056399, \"rank\": 0.02334994816974991, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are lifting the strike warning, there is a majority deal\\\" among unions who threatened the walkout, said Rachid Eddaidj, secretary general of the CFDT union's branch at Paris Airports (ADP).\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 609, \"end\": 613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Democratic_Confederation_of_Labour\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CFDT\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q178790\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Democratic_Confederation_of_Labour\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Democratic_Confederation_of_Labour\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unions had called for a stoppage on Wednesday to press for bigger Olympics bonuses and staff recruitment.\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They have now secured a \\\"standardised bonus for every worker at ADP\\\" as well as extras for those helping with Olympic delegations and their baggage, management said.\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 927, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Along with Paris' train stations, ADP-operated Charles de Gaulle and Orly airports will be the main gateways into France for foreign visitors to the Olympics, as well as athletes and their equipment.\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 1128, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 940, \"end\": 945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999188276, \"rank\": 8.118055888728175e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 976, \"end\": 993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Gaulle_Airport\", \"score\": 0.9999199783638036, \"rank\": 8.002660690625069e-05, \"text\": \"Charles de Gaulle\", \"types\": [\"Q1248784\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Gaulle_Airport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Gaulle_Airport\"}, {\"begin\": 1043, \"end\": 1049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9976223690693563, \"rank\": 0.0007988166459301086, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The company has spent 50 million euros ($54 million) upgrading its infrastructure and French authorities are deploying extra resources to make the experience as smooth and safe as possible.\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1216, \"end\": 1222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9720360590056399, \"rank\": 0.02334994816974991, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Charles de Gaulle is expecting peaks of 300,000 travellers passing through in a single day, well above the summer daily average of 200,000.\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1460, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1321, \"end\": 1338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Gaulle_Airport\", \"score\": 0.9999199783638036, \"rank\": 8.002660690625069e-05, \"text\": \"Charles de Gaulle\", \"types\": [\"Q1248784\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Gaulle_Airport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Gaulle_Airport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The busiest days are expected to come after the Olympics closing ceremony on August 11 when spectators, officials and most of the 10,000 athletes will head home.\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Once out of the terminals, regular travellers will find multi-lingual \\\"welcome teams\\\" offering advice on travel and buying tickets at the train stations.\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Police are also set to step up patrols against pickpockets.\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1839, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"AFP  \\u00a9Channels Incorporated Limited.\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1877, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 1898, \"entities\": []}]}"